Troubleshooting
Issue: "Module not found" errors

Solution: Ensure virtual environment is activated: source venv/bin/activate
Issue: Permission denied errors

Solution: Check file permissions: chmod +x test_runner.py
Issue: Timeout not working

Solution: Verify timeout parameter is passed to subprocess.run()
Issue: Commands not being blocked

Solution: Review validation logic and ensure whitelist is properly checked
Issue: Logging not working

Solution: Verify logs directory exists: mkdir -p logs
